## Sampling and Influence

The song's opening was used in the Belgium Dance act Oxy's 1992 single "The Feeling." Additionally, the lyrics of the chorus were interpolated in the 1995 song "Tragedy" by [RZA](/RZA) from the [Wu-Tang Clan](/Wu-Tang_Clan). The lyrics "Walk with me, like lovers do/Talk to me, like lovers do" were also used in [Platinum Weird](/Platinum_Weird)'s song "[Taking Chances](/Taking_Chances_(song))", which was co-written by Stewart and later covered by [Celine Dion](/Celine_Dion) on her 2007 album of the same name.

